name: The Abhinaya villa
address: Hotel near Payung Rafting 450m, Jl. Begawan Giri, Melinggih, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1:
Really cheap, nice rooms.

However it is shared with other guests (only private rooms) And the Wifi was not working flawlessly at the time

However it is quite far away from Ubud (30-40min by car)
review 2: It was really beautiful. Very clean and owner of the villa was really very friendly. But it would be nice if they provide us some toiletries like shampoo, shower gel, brush etc. Otherwise it was good.
review 3: The villa was amizing, has big rooms, big living room, amazing environment, and superb friendly nice owner, really recommended.
review 4: This villa is very comfortable for guests who want to relax the view is very nice
review 5: Very nice and clean place with delightful owner. Fully recommended
